      "content": "but the snack idea makes me worried about my levels being too high later. if i just skip the basal dose tonight, my body will just naturally use what's left in my system, right? it seems way safer to avoid the risk of a crash than to take a full dose when i haven't even had a real meal. can't i just skip it this one time and be fine?",
